                        <interp inst="t18380917-name-153" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS LINTHWAITE</persName>
                  </hi>. I was in Mr. George Everingham's, my em<lb></lb>ployer's shop—these things were brought back, this one pair of trowsers and waistcoats were in a hat—these others were brought in afterwards they are all my master's, there is a private mark on them.</p>
